 "html": "{{letter_head}}\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"\" class=\"fields-table-structured\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{doc.party_name}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">Pro Forma No:</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{doc.party_name}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"><br>{{doc.address_display}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">Pro Forma Date:</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{doc.get_formatted(\"transaction_date\")}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<table class=\"table-structured\" border=\"1\">\r\n\t<thead>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 5%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Qty</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 15%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Part Number</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 20%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Description</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 15%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Serial No</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 12%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Unit Cost</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 11%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Total Year 1</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 11%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Total Year 2</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th style=\"width: 11%\" class=\"table-structured-labels\">Total Year 3</th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</thead>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t{% for row in doc.items %}\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values text-right\">{{row.qty}}</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values\">{{row.custom_part_number}}</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values\">{{row.description}}</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values\">{{row.custom_serial_no}}</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values text-right\">\r\n\t\t\t\t{{row.get_formatted(\"rate\")}}\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values text-right\">\r\n\t\t\t\t{{row.get_formatted(\"amount\")}}\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values text-right\">\r\n\t\t\t\t{{row.get_formatted(\"custom_year_total_2\")}}\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-structured-values text-right\">\r\n\t\t\t\t{{row.get_formatted(\"custom_year_total_3\")}}\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t{% endfor %}\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Note:</p>\r\n<table style=\"\" class=\"fields-table-structured\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">1.</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tThis Quote is Valid for 1 WEEK (validity period changes per\r\n\t\t\t\t\tcustomer/deal)\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">2.</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tOSTEC is Exempted from 3% Withholding TAX on GOODS and 7.5%\r\n\t\t\t\t\tWithholding Tax on Services and Installation.\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">3.</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tPayment Terms: {{doc.party_name}} standard payment terms i.e. payment\r\n\t\t\t\t\twithin 14 working days after delivery. {NB ( changes pe customer/deal\r\n\t\t\t\t\t)}\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">4.</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tDelivery Period: 8 -12+ WEEKS after approval (changes per\r\n\t\t\t\t\tcustomer/deal) OSTEC is Exempted from 3% Withholding TAX on GOODS and\r\n\t\t\t\t\t7.5% Withholding Tax on Services and Installation.\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style=\"\" class=\"fields-table-structured\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">Sub Total [1] USD</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values text-right\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{doc.get_formatted(\"total\")}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t{% for t_row in doc.taxes %}\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{t_row.description}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values text-right\" style=\"width:25%; padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{t_row.get_formatted(\"tax_amount\")}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t{% endfor %}\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-labels\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">Total USD</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td class=\"fields-table-structured-values text-right\" style=\"padding:1px !important; margin:1px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"\">{{doc.get_formatted(\"grand_total\")}}</div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n",
